                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per 10 minutes",
                    "effect": "Strike with the *morphing weapon*, choosing one of the following benefits to apply to the Strike. \n* **Reach** Increase the reach by 5 feet.\n* **Shift** The weapon's damage becomes your choice of bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing instead of its normal type.\n* **Take** If the Strike hits, you can attempt to Disarm or Steal from your target immediately after as a reaction.\n* **Weigh** Gain a status bonus to the damage roll equal to the weapon's number of damage dice.",
